abstract: Visa, the world’s largest credit-card network, said on Monday there is a 95 percent chance it will complete its initial public offering by Oct. 10, Reuters reported citing a quarterly filing.
lead_paragraph: Visa, the world’s largest credit-card network, said on Monday there is a 95 percent chance it will complete its initial public offering by Oct. 10, Reuters reported citing a quarterly filing.

headline.main: Visa Eyes October Deadline for I.P.O.
